# DESCRIPTION
# Find the exact value of logn(A), where A = n^k.
#
# ENDDESCRIPTION
## DBsubject(Algebra)
## DBchapter(Exponential and logarithmic expressions and functions)
## DBsection(Properties of logarithms)
## Institution(John Wiley & Sons)
## MLT(EvaluateBasicLogs)
## Level(2)
## MO(1)
## TitleText1('Calculus')
## AuthorText1('Anton')
## EditionText1('9')
## Section1('0.5')
